This is a sample file used to test the Secure File Storage System.

You can use this file to try out the encryption and decryption features:

1. Run "python main.py"
2. Choose option 1 (Encrypt File)
3. Enter the path: sample_files/sample.txt
4. Choose option 2 (Decrypt File) and select the resulting .enc file
5. Check the decrypted_files/ folder for the restored file

Feel free to edit this file or add your own files to test with!
